item.description: I set up a new document repository. I was tired of having to refind everythign I was looking for. So I set up a place that has everything together. wee. I am excited. now only if it was nicer and better. hehe. soon. my dear… soon.. check it out at nata2.info… I found some good stuff to post: Mac osX hacks and Chicago wireless access points..
